{"event": "tool.sampling.request", "frame": {"jsonrpc": "2.0", "id": "1cfcc36e8a8e4775bb83c26863a4d598", "method": "sampling/createMessage", "params": {"messages": [{"role": "user", "content": {"type": "text", "text": "请整理下面按添加顺序排列的笔记。\n要求：\n1. 给出简洁、准确的整体总结。\n2. 提取主要主题和明确的待办事项。\n3. 不添加原笔记中不存在的信息。\n4. 直接返回总结内容，不要添加无关前言。\n\n笔记：\n1. [添加顺序 1] 明天跟客户 follow up\n2. [添加顺序 2] 修复登录 bug\n3. [添加顺序 3] 准备 Workshop 内容"}}], "maxTokens": 400, "includeContext": "none", "_clientTimeoutS": 60.0, "systemPrompt": "你是一名简洁、准确的笔记整理助手。", "metadata": {"executa_invoke_id": "protocol-smoke-invoke-1", "tool": "summarize_notes", "note_count": 3}}}}
